      </article>

      <article class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2">
        <a class="infobulle" href="/rayons/boissons"><img src="img/vignette-vin.jpg" alt="Boisson" title="Photo by Ylanite Koppens from Pexels">
        <p>Boissons</p></a>
      </article>

      <article class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2">
        <a class="infobulle" href="/rayons/boulangerie"><img src="img/vignette-pain.jpg" alt="Pain" title="Photo from Pexels">
        <p>Boulangerie - pâtisserie</p></a>
      </article>

      <article class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2">
